# [pyScript](https://github.com/n138-kz/pyScript)

## github repository initial setup

1. "Actions secrets and variables" > "Repository secrets" 移動し、`DISCORD_WEBHOOK_URL` を設定  
  値は Discord webhook url を設定

```
DISCORD_WEBHOOK_URL
```
